{"tid":1169772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逃犯條例, 湯渣華引述張曉明四種犯罪","createTime":"2019-05-24T15:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T06:11:26.000Z","uid":76310,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"46530ca1a51d40eb8846c1e4b45063bb058b6c62","tid":1169772,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:04:39.000Z","msg":"逃犯條例, 湯渣華引述張曉明四種犯罪:<br />\n<br />\n1. 強国人在強国犯罪潛逃到香港的, 主要是指強国貪官, 強国奸商, 強国土豪<br />\n2.香港居民在強国犯罪然後潛逃到香港的<br />\n3.強国公民或外國人在外國針對中国国家公民犯罪而身在香港的<br />\n4.香港居民在香港觸犯危害国家安全罪<br />\n<br />\n即是全部人包括<br />\n可以捉貪官抄家, 可以捉外資抄家, 可以捉港豬抄家, 可以捉地產霸權抄家, 捉邊個抄家都得<br />\n<br />\n捉貪官抄家, 外資抄家, 港商比人抄家, 港豬比人抄家<br />\n所有香港人一齊冧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb644d104e19ac7fc69ac3c198f551fa4255e951","tid":1169772,"uid":225130,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:06:17.000Z","msg":"其實唔駛咁煩 是但搵條罪砌你<br />\n原來係香港合法既野係大陸唔合法"},{"pid":"d924980c4a81ca1fbd34be1e1aa99cfb76d8c74e","tid":1169772,"uid":76310,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:06:36.000Z","msg":"圖窮匕見<br />\n強国要強姦香港, 香港玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8794cfe290e574f547ee9d2611abe9df3e2fe9ed","tid":1169772,"uid":57787,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:11:31.000Z","msg":"剩係4已經死得啦，講句天滅支共、打倒共產黨已經犯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d264f8cb85be3b5ac1e21c59a9b3634e883f4a59","tid":1169772,"uid":35580,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T15:12:58.000Z","msg":"香港居民在香港觸犯危害国家安全罪<br />\n<br />\n23條<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4303c50445a5f2129425812d65230ea32bd48c2c","tid":1169772,"uid":33874,"like":15,"dislike":0